00:32:50.020 --> 00:32:53.690
all, I don't want to
support that because it's

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:58.980
so far the worst form of online
harassment that I've experienced.

00:32:59.040 --> 00:33:02.500
- Yeah. There's a lot of toxicity in
