00:35:13.360 --> 00:35:16.590
an empty account ready to be
rename- renamed to Claude

00:35:16.660 --> 00:35:20.400
Bot, and the other one I renamed
to Mod Bot. So, I pressed

00:35:20.420 --> 00:35:24.360
rename there, I pressed rename
there, and in those five seconds,

00:35:24.400 --> 00:35:26.940
they stole the account name.

00:35:27.020 --> 00:35:30.890
Literally, the five seconds of
dragging the mouse over there and

00:35:30.940 --> 00:35:33.680
pressing rename there was too long.

00:35:33.740 --> 00:35:33.980
- Wow.

00:35:34.020 --> 00:35:37.560
- Because there's no... Those systems... I
mean, you would expect that they have some

00:35:37.580 --> 00:35:41.540
protection or, like, an
automatic forwarding, but

00:35:41.560 --> 00:35:44.970
there's nothing like that.
And I didn't know that

00:35:46.140 --> 00:35:49.580
they're not just good at harassment,
they're also really good

00:35:49.720 --> 00:35:51.580
at using scripts and tools.

00:35:51.640 --> 00:35:52.040
- Yeah.

00:35:53.279 --> 00:35:56.279
- So, yeah. So, suddenly,
like, the old account

00:35:56.340 --> 00:35:59.920
was promoting new tokens
and serving malware.

00:36:01.540 --> 00:36:05.120
