- Yeah. I think two MacBooks are real.
The main one that drives the two big

01:32:40.358 --> 01:32:46.478
screens, and there's another MacBook
that I sometimes use for, for testing.

01:32:46.518 --> 01:32:48.317
- So two big screens.

01:32:48.568 --> 01:32:53.617
- I'm a big fan of anti-glare.
So I have this wide Dell

01:32:54.778 --> 01:32:58.018
that's anti-glare and you can
just fit a lot of terminals

01:32:58.338 --> 01:33:00.148
side-by-side. I usually have

01:33:01.238 --> 01:33:04.898
a terminal and at the bottom, I- I-
