01:33:04.958 --> 01:33:08.728
of actual terminal, mostly
because when I started,

01:33:08.798 --> 01:33:15.378
I- I sometimes made the mistake and I- I
mi- I mixed up the- the windows, and I

01:33:15.438 --> 01:33:19.338
gave... I- I prompted
in the wrong project,

01:33:19.858 --> 01:33:23.818
and then the agent ran off for, like,
20 minutes, manically trying to

01:33:23.858 --> 01:33:27.758
understand what I could have meant,
being completely confused because it

01:33:27.798 --> 01:33:31.418
was the wrong folder. And sometimes
they've been clever enough to, like,

01:33:32.418 --> 01:33:35.978
get out of the workday and, like, figure
out that, oh, you meant another project.

01:33:35.998 --> 01:33:36.278
- Mm-hmm.

01:33:36.298 --> 01:33:39.258
- But oftentimes, it's just,
like, what? You know?

01:33:40.018 --> 01:33:43.178
Like, fit your- f- put yourself in the
