01:33:43.198 --> 01:33:43.258
- Yeah

01:33:43.318 --> 01:33:47.268
- ... and then get, like, a super weird
something that does not exist and then just,

01:33:47.298 --> 01:33:53.098
like... They're problem solvers so they
try really hard and always feel bad.

01:33:54.018 --> 01:34:00.117
So it's always, um, Codex and, like,
a little bit of actual terminal. Also

01:34:00.138 --> 01:34:03.838
helpful because I don't
use work trees. I like to

01:34:03.958 --> 01:34:07.898
