01:34:14.778 --> 01:34:18.687
Like, I don't even need plan mode, you know?
There's so many people that come from Claude

01:34:18.738 --> 01:34:22.718
Code and they're so, so Claude-pilled and,
like, have their workflows and they come

01:34:22.738 --> 01:34:26.378
