01:34:26.418 --> 01:34:29.438
necessary because you
just- you just talk to the

01:34:29.478 --> 01:34:33.298
agent. And when it's... when
you... there's a few trigger

01:34:33.338 --> 01:34:37.548
words how you can prevent it from building.
You're like, "Discuss, give me options."

01:34:37.558 --> 01:34:38.258
- Mm-hmm.

01:34:38.298 --> 01:34:42.538
- Don't write code yet if you wanna be
very specific, you just talk and then

01:34:44.238 --> 01:34:47.878
when you're ready, then- then just write,
