01:34:47.898 --> 01:34:50.438
And then maybe it goes off for
20 minutes and does the thing.

01:34:50.458 --> 01:34:54.848
- You know what I really like is asking
it, "Do you have any questions for me?"

01:34:54.898 --> 01:34:58.778
- Yeah. And again, like, Claude
Code has a UI that kind

01:34:58.818 --> 01:35:02.778
of guides you through that. It's kind of
