01:38:17.098 --> 01:38:21.367
this, but this corner case could be
something write more tests." Um,

01:38:22.218 --> 01:38:25.827
documentation. Now that the
whole context is full, like, I

01:38:25.878 --> 01:38:32.898
mean, I'm not saying my documentation
is great, but it's not bad.

01:38:32.918 --> 01:38:37.117
And pretty much everything
is, is LM generated. So, so,

01:38:38.178 --> 01:38:41.258
